I";<p>Summary of <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1611.06172.pdf">this</a> paper on
parallelizing word2vec model training on Intel CPUs.</p>

<ul>
  <li>convert level-1 blas to level-3 by using
    <ul>
      <li>shared negative samples</li>
      <li>group multiple input contexts words for a given target word</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>for scaling to multi-nodes
    <ul>
      <li>model update frequency is tied to word frequency</li>
      <li>reduce starting learning rate as the number of nodes</li>
      <li>m-weighted sampling updates</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
